We would like to express our sincere gratitude to Mr. Strebel Dominik André, Dr. Pak Wai Chan, Prof. Dr. Zhiwen Luo and Mr. Xiaoxiong Xie for their assistance in air temperature data collection. 
Mr. Strebel Dominik André has helped us collect data in Zurich and Montreal; Dr. Pak Wai Chan has helped us collect data in Hong Kong; Prof. Dr. Zhiwen Luo and Mr. Xiaoxiong Xie have helped us collect data in London.
